sentences: She became a radio announcer in 1954, and soon starting writing her own music.
She retired from performing in 1973 and focused on teaching and researching the art of Hakka hill songs.
Lai founded an eponymous Hakka folk music troupe in 1993.
She received the Jury Award at the 2011 Golden Melody Awards.
Lai died aged 82 on 18 January 2015, at home in Zhongli.
